<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Activate Your IpTruck Account</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f39c12;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #27ae60;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .activation-code {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üîê Account Activation Required</h1>
        <p>Complete your IpTruck registration</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= contactName %>,</h2>
        
        <p>Welcome to IpTruck! Your company <strong><%= companyName %></strong> has been successfully registered, but we need to verify your account before you can start using our platform.</p>
        
        <p>To activate your account, please click the button below:</p>
        
        <center>
            <a href="<%= activationUrl %>" class="button">Activate Account</a>
        </center>
        
        <p>Alternatively, you can use this activation code:</p>
        
        <div class="activation-code">
            <%= activationCode %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> This activation link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons. Please activate your account as soon as possible.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>What happens after activation?</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>‚úÖ Access to your personalized dashboard</li>
            <li>üöõ Start booking trucks or receiving booking requests</li>
            <li>üìä View analytics and reports</li>
            <li>üí¨ Contact support and other users</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>If you're having trouble clicking the activation button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #3498db;"><%= activationUrl %></p>
        
        <p><strong>Need Help?</strong></p>
        <p>If you didn't create this account or need assistance, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@iptruck.com">support@iptruck.com</a></p>
        
        <p>Thank you for choosing IpTruck!</p>
        <p>The IpTruck Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>¬© 2024 IpTruck. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This email was sent to activate your account.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
